@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white

title STEMgraph-API Architecture

actor User

rectangle "setup" as setup
rectangle "stemgraph-parser" as parser
rectangle "api" as api

database "data-volume" as data
database "gh-credentials" as gh

cloud "GitHub API" as github

User --> setup : 1. auth
setup --> gh : stores token

User --> parser : 2. run
parser --> gh : uses token
parser --> github : fetches repos
parser --> data : writes jsonld.json

User --> api : 3. start
api --> data : reads jsonld.json
api --> User : http://localhost:8000

@enduml
